commit.message:
Identify TRUNCATE as DDL, REVOKE/GRANT as DCL keywords.

See #719 as well.
CI: Reset max-complexity to current default.
Switch to hatch and replace tox.
Add new group for MySQL specific keywords.
Improve formatting of statements with JSON operators (fixes #542).
Add support for some of the JSON operators (fixes #682).

Drop support for Python < 3.8.

Also update tox.ini and Github actions:
- unpin some dependencies required for older Python versions
- update action versions to latest version
Improve splitting of Transact SQL when using GO keyword (fixes #762).
Ensure nested ordered identifiers are grouped (fixes #745)
allow operators to procede dollar quoted strings
Add option to remove trailing semicolon when splitting (fixes #742).
